channel.title: Need help with a few things [eclipse 639 bases]
channel.description:
First of all I edited "home" command to my new home coordinates which is catherby and I saved and compiled but it won't work. I don't know why. It even does the same for staffzone i change coordinates and it won't work. In fact, every commands I try to add fails. (added a bunch before so idk whats wrong)and when i compile i get no errors.
Also, how can i add titles like "junior cadet" or "owner" or even "head moderator" in front of somebodys name ?
Finally, how can I make a shop use tickets or vote points or even pk points unless of money ?
Thanks you very much !
Kiss my feet.
